--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.5.1 (2019-11-11)
E: Minor template improvement (dynamic path)

* Version 2.5.0 (2019-10-21)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 2.4.0 (2019-09-06)
F: Update 'alertmanager' to version '0.19.0'

* Version 2.3.0 (2019-07-09)
F: Update 'alertmanager' to version '0.18.0'

* Version 2.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.1.0 (2019-05-05)
F: Update 'alertmanager' to version '0.17.0'

* Version 2.0.2 (2019-02-06)
B: Fix templating issue (add missing closing bracket)
E: Minor cosmetic template improvement

* Version 2.0.1 (2019-02-05)
E: Use Jinja2 argument 'indentfirst' instead of 'first' (support older Jinja2 versions)

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-02-04)
C: Redesign 'alertmanager_config' option (alter config variable to string)

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-01-31)
F: Update 'alertmanager' to version '0.16.1'

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-01-24)
F: Update 'alertmanager' to version '0.16.0'

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-13)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-12-11)
E: Minor Jinja2 syntax improvements
E: Move 'alertmanager-current.link' task from 'install' to 'enable'

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-11-28)
F: Initial release
